    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Esther \"Mamaine\" Cartagena",
          "underline": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Esther Cartagena Castrillon, also known as \"Mamaine,\" is a chef, cultural organizer, and politician. She received notoriety for her work in her restaurant \"El Refugio de Mamaine,\" where she preserves traditional Afro-Peruvian culinary practices in Guayabo, El Carmen, Chincha, Peru. In addition to her work at her restaurant, she has served as an advocate for the rights of Afro-Peruvian women and has experience in political spaces, having served as the Regional Councilor of Chincha.\n\n "
        }
      ]
