    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Eva Ayllon",
          "underline": true
        },
        {
          "text": "\nEva Ayllón is one of the most iconic Afro-Peruvian singers, internationally recognized for her powerful voice and her contributions to the global visibility of Afro-Peruvian music. She has played a central role in popularizing genres such as landó, festejo, and other coastal rhythms, bringing Afro-Peruvian traditions to major international stages. \n\n"
        }
      ]
